# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic
Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]

## [1.0.0]
### Added
    - Basic Literate Programming File & Repo.
    - Hitlist of Software I'd Like to Package (.hitlist).
    - `keyring` branch.
    - Guix Authorizations for both rodnchr and yewscion GPG Keys.
    - Standard Project Files.
    - Packages:
        - `adlmidi`
        - `newlisp`
        - `owl-lisp`
        - `gnu-apl` (alternative to upstream, due to slow bugfixes)
        - `carp`
        - `ghc-open-browser`
        - `sbcl-stumpwm-battery-portable`
        - `orca-music`
        - `uxn`
        - `texlive-latex-lwarp`
        - `texlive-generic-ifptex`
        - `texlive-latex-xpatch`
        - `texlive-latex-catchfile`
        - `texlive-latex-comment`
        - `texlive-generic-xstring`
        - `texlive-biblatex-apa`
        - `texlive-latex-setspace`
        - `texlive-latex-endfloat`
        - `texlive-latex-minted`
        - `texlive-latex-fvextra`
        - `texlive-latex-lineno`
        - `texlive-latex-datetime2`
        - `texlive-tracklang`
        - `texlive-latex-datetime2-english`
        - `xindy`
        - `texlive-latex-everyhook`
        - `texlive-svn-prov`
        - `texlive-latex-newfloat`
        - `texlive-latex-printlen`
        - `texlive-latex-cleveref`
        - `texlive-latex-readablecv`
        - `texlive-latex-memoir`
        - `texlive-latex-lipsum`
        - `genpro`
        - `pagr`
        - `guile-cdr255`
        - `yewscion-scripts`
        - `python-pygments-lexer-pseudocode-std`
    - Work In Progress Packages (Not ready, not public):
        - `leiningen` (due to upstream choices, compiling from source is very difficult).
    - Problem Packages (removal ASAP):
        - `leiningen-ng` (nonguix version due to difficulties packaging leiningen).
        - `leiningen-jar` (nonguix version due to difficulties packaging leiningen).
### Changed
    - README.md now includes introduction information.
    - Repo now under AGPL-3.0 instead of LGPL-3.0.
    - Guix Authorizations (Added Above) now in LP File.
    - Refactored all scattered modules into 4 topical ones under `cdr255/`.
### Removed
    - LP file, since it was unnecessary.
    - Hitlist of software, as it was unneeded.
    - Packages:
        - `hledger-ui` (I didn't use it, and it was slowing me down due to
          haskell).
        - `ghc-vty` (only needed for `hledger-ui`).
        - `ghc-brick` (only needed for `hledger-ui`).

[1.0.0]: https://git.sr.ht/~yewscion/yewscion-guix-channel/refs/1.0.0
[Unreleased]: https://git.sr.ht/~yewscion/yewscion-guix-channel/log

